															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser deleted" data-id="1324229"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/common--images/avatars/default/a16.png" alt=""/>(account deleted)</span> <span class="odate time_1478731221 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">09 Nov 2016 22:40</span>
														</div>
