			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2688398">
									

<p>I must be missing some incredibly crucial detail, because whilst others are praising this conclusion to the Kalinin proposal, I'm left with a complete lack of understanding at what the hell is/was going on. All i've really gotten from this is &quot;End of the Veil&quot; mixed with &quot;Suffering for the greater good because&quot; - I don't understand <em>why</em> these planets are designed to be torture places. I don't understand who is benefiting from the Planet of Hands/Eyes/Flesh. Most importantly, I don't understand how any of this relates to humanity, earth, or the Foundationverse in general.</p>
<p>Again, I must be missing something crucial, but to me this is just coming across as 'anomalous stuff happens because'.</p>

