			<div class="content" id="post-content-2688462">
									

<p>I feel unsatisfied and disappointed after reading this. It's like Clef's proposal and all the tales related to it plus SCP-093 with admittedly great character building. Also, this doesn't explain the evolving skips, the side effects of SCP-2798, or what SCP-001 really is.</p>
<p>You need like a whole other set of tales to explain all of this.</p>

